quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,20,Aey eman walo! Allah ka aur uss kay rasool ka kaha mano aur uss (ka kaha mannay) say roo-gardani mat kero suntay jantay huye
  8,21,Aur tum unn logon ki tarah mat hona jo dawa to kertay hain kay hum ney sunn liya halankay woh suntay (sunatay kuch) nahi
  8,22,Be-shak bad tareen khaleeq Allah Taalaa kay nazdeek woh log hain jo behray hain goongay hain jo kay (zara) nahi samajhtay
  8,23,Aur agar Allah Taalaa inn mein koi khoobi dekhta to inn ko sunnay ki tofiq dey deta aur agar inn ko abb suna dey to zaroor roo gardani keren gay bey rukhi kertay huye
  8,24,Aey eman walo! Tum Allah aur rasool kay kehney ko baja lao jabkay rasool tum ko tumhari zindagi bakhsh cheez ki taraf bulatay hon. Aur jaan rakho kay Allah Taalaa aadmi kay aur uss kay qalb kay darmiyan aarr bann jaya kerta hai aur bila shuba tum sab ko Allah hi kay pass jama hona hai
  8,25,Aur tum aisay wabaal say bacho! Kay jo khaas ker sirf unhi logon per waqiya na hoga jo tum say inn gunhaon kay muratakib huye hain aur yeh jaan rakho kay Allah sakht saza denay wala hai
  8,26,Aur uss halat ko yaad kero! Jab tum zamin mein qaleel thay kamzor shumar kiye jatay thay. Iss andeshay mein rehtay thay kay tum ko log noch khasot na len so Allah ney tum ko rehney ki jagah di aur tum ko apni nusrat say qooat di aur tum ko nafees nafees cheezen ata farmaeen takay tum shukar kero
  8,27,Aey eman walo! Tum Allah aur rasool (kay huqooq) mein jantay huye khayanat mat kero aur apni qaabil-e-hifazat cheezon mein khayanat na kero
  8,28,Aur tum iss baat ko jaan rakho kay tumharay amwaal aur tumhari aulad aik imtehan ki cheez hai. Aur iss baat ko bhi jaan rakho kay Allah Taalaa kay pass bara bhari ajar hai